quran[5]{c,v,t,f}:
  22,1,"Dadow! Iska jira (Ciqaabka) Rabbigiin! Hubaal, Gariirka Saacadda (Qiyaame) waa wax weyn oo daran.",""
  22,2,"Maalinta aad arkeysaan haweeney kasta oo ilmo nuujinaysa iyadoo ka tegi ilmahay naaska nuujinaysay, oo haweeney walboo uur leh dhicin waxay uurka ku siddo, waxaadna arki dadka oo (ah sida kuwo) sakhraansan, mana aha kuwo sakhraansan, Cadaabka Alle baase ah mid Daran.",""
  22,3,"Waxaa ka mid ah dadka mid ka dooda arrinka Alle cilmi la’aan, raacana Shaydaan kastoo madax adag.",""
  22,4,"Waxaa loo qoray in qofkii raaca  (sheydaan) oo saaxiib ka yeesha inuu lumiyo oo ku hago cadaabka hurka badan.",""
  22,5,"Dadow! Haddaad shaki ka qabtaan soo bixinta (iilka layska soo saari), Waxaanu idinka abuurnay carro, haddana dhibic mani ah, haddana xinjir, haddana
